<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA78">
<l>araṅkamāyp pēykkāṭṭi lāṭuvāṉ vāḷā</l>
<l>viraṅkumō vevvuyirkku mēḻā - yiraṅkumē</l>
<l>leṉṉāka vaiyāṉṟā ṉevvulaka mīntaḷiyāṉ</l>
<l>paṉṉā ḷirantāṟ paṇintu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who dances on the demonic cremation ground as a stage silently,</l>
<l>will he feel pity of any living being, you fool? If he were to feel pity,</l>
<l>will he not put in any effort?  Will he not give [and] provide any world,</l>
<l>if one humbly begs for many days?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
